":"2017-08-02T21:31:32.000Z","msg":"返香港發展待遇係點"},{"pid":"7955af8c7c9e2ed5d36d6cbac0cfbfcd9128ae50","tid":345163,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T21:32:20.000Z","msg":"咩叫好難先<br />\n係你既行業根本拎唔到定其他野影響<br />\n<br />\n去外國讀書如果唔係為左讀香港讀唔到既野/追求高質素師資<br />\n而拎唔到居留權就返香港<br />\n我都會覺得係完全浪費錢"},{"pid":"d4da73223f64eb4d5dfde9fb176d0a4d66a0f956","tid":345163,"uid":70411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T21:44:29.000Z","msg":"答佢唔係唔返 只係想試下喺當地發展一排 知道屋企好辛苦供我讀書 但我真係想留低試下 畢竟呢度嘅氣氛比較適合我呢科嘅發展 等我事業有成再帶你哋過黎 等我阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618fd9a006440054351447be573afd4e8038a7f5","tid":345163,"uid":79111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T21:46:12.000Z","msg":"其實個faculty係咪好大 成日聽到有人去瑞士讀hotel man<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b87e42df58e51d4a0a14e279cee7e4323680bb","tid":345163,"uid":3287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T21:56:22.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 太掛住香港返咗嚟<br />\n而家打緊份閪工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b32428a84e1d01e71f6633bb4e3d76d08b196b6","tid":345163,"uid":56466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T21:57:35.000Z","msg":"SEG? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d711796bee1086659836131d208a090d5a77c1","tid":345163,"uid":56051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T22:00:02.000Z","msg":"機會只有一次 你返左香港就冇<br />\n反而你留喺出面 搵到錢一樣可以匯錢返香港俾家用 而且隨時都可以返香港探親/搵工 <br />\n條命你自己嘅 自己決定啦"},{"pid":"4d2476a10bed94732a6ca5c353e1491c44e1a4f8","tid":345163,"uid":47941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T00:56:40.000Z","msg":"香港做酒店狗也不屌<br />\n做住pt先囉，始終屋企重要<br />\n去得外國都係要睇屋企架啦，佢地供嘅"},{"pid":"f7d6cdcd6fcde9a173f23292d25304a8d2821202","tid":345163,"uid":16914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T